videos.description: Kyle Shurmur steps up in the pocket and finds Jared Pinkney for a 17-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Shurmur connects with Pinkney for 17-yard TD

videos.description: Ty Chandler blows past the Vanderbilt defense for a 75-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Chandler takes off for a 75-yard Tennessee TD

videos.description: Kyle Shurmur finds Kalija Lipscomb down the sideline who makes the catch one handed for a 23-yard gain.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt's Lipscomb hauls in one-handed catch

videos.description: Kyle Shurmur throws a deep ball to Amir Abdur-Rahman who hauls it in for a 26-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Abdur-Rahman lays out for 26-yard TD

videos.description: Vanderbilt head coach Derek Mason and the Vanderbilt team celebrate after taking down Tennessee 38-13.
videos.headline: Vanderbilt celebrates with bowling strike after beating Vols
